node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Anaheim Ducks on July 29, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'DUCKS HOCKEY PULT CLUB Health DORNIL TOGETHER I'm excited. Obviously by signing a contract it shows my belief. This is group that thought took good strides last year. We have a little ways to go, and we've got some things to do. Hopefully (EVP/GM Bob Murray) can do little bit more and fill some holes for us. My belief is extremely high going into this year, and my expectation is high. I'd like to take that big step forward this year." RYAN GETZLAF ON HIS BELIEF IN HOW THE DUCKS WILL COMPETE LN THE UPCOMING SEASON'.

node.text: Steve Carroll, John Ahlers and @guyhebert31 recap our Saturday at the #NHLDraft. #DucksDraft presented by @Honda

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Anaheim Ducks on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'DUCKS HOCKEY PUNT CLUB Health TOGETHER Josh was a good player in the USHL, but his skating has taken another step. He was outstanding for UMass in the NCAA playoffs, and he was a big part of their success this year down the stretch. He's big body, competitive, strong on faceoffs and he's got some finish around the net. He likes to get his nose dirty. think he fits well even though he's an older player with a 2001 birthday." ASSISTANT MARTIN MADDEN ON THE SELECTION OF JOSH LOPINA 2020 DRAFT HONDA'.

node.text: 🗣️🗣️🗣️ Hear it straight from our Assistant G.M. #DucksDraft presented by @Honda.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Anaheim Ducks on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'DUCKS HOCKEY PUNT CLUB Health TOGETHER Josh was a good player in the USHL, but his skating has taken another step. He was outstanding for UMass in the NCAA playoffs, and he was a big part of their success this year down the stretch. He's big body, competitive, strong on faceoffs and he's got some finish around the net. He likes to get his nose dirty. think he fits well even though he's an older player with a 2001 birthday." ASSISTANT MARTIN MADDEN ON THE SELECTION OF JOSH LOPINA 2020 DRAFT HONDA'.

Photo by Anaheim Ducks on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'DUCKS HOCKEY PURTET CLUB LOAL TOGETHER He's a sniper. He's got really good awareness of the ice in the offensive zone, and he's got a really good release, really accurate shot. We were looking for a player like him today for sure. He anticipates, reads the play very well. He's very aware of what the options are, very good at reading where rebounds are going to go." ASSISTANT MARTIN MADDEN ON THE SELECTION OF SASHA PASTUJOV 2021 DRAFT HONDA'.

Photo by Anaheim Ducks on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'DUCKS HOCKEY PAN CLUB Health TOGETHER I can tell you that Sudsie (Ducks goalie coach Sudarshan Maharaj) loves him. He's huge, athletic, just on the upswing of his development. He's a year older than most of these guys and took the lead the last half of his team's schedule. He's just getting started." ASSISTANT MARTIN MADDEN ON THE SELECTION OF GAGE ALEXANDER 2021 DRAGS HONDA'.

Photo by Anaheim Ducks on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'DUCKS HOCKEY PULTT CLUO Health TOGETHER I think our three American scouts are really excited about him. High character, high drive, really fast, really good skill, captain material. He's a dynamic player and he's got some upside." ASSISTANT MARTIN MADDEN ON THE SELECTION OF KYLE KUKKONEN 2021 DRAFO HONDA'.

Photo by Anaheim Ducks on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'DUCKS HOCKEY PUNTT CLUB TOGETHER He's probably closer to the way Jared Spurgeon [of Minnesota] plays, similar in how they help their teams play fast, get back for pucks quickly, move it up quickly, join the offense, dynamic overall. I think it's always good to move the puck to the forwards quickly and get that second layer of attack, and he fits that mold for sure." ASSISTANT MARTIN MADDEN ON THE SELECTION OF OLEN ZELLWEGER 2021 DRAFT HONDA'.
